VALUES ('the-force-edition-yoda', 'The Force Edition - Yoda',
        'Planets swirl, stars twinkle, hmmm. Moon cheese, space stew, yes. Rocket riddles, comet cookies, wise you become, laugh we must.',
        '<p>In the galaxy far, twinkling stars and swirling nebulas, wise and ancient secrets hold they do. Orbiting moons, glowing they are, like lanterns in cosmic night. Whispers of the Force, through the astral winds they float, speaking of destiny and paths unseen.</p>
<p>Hmm, strong in this one, the Force is. Amongst the stars, adventures await, they do. Old Jedi texts, hidden in the starlight, secrets of the ancients they reveal. Patience, young Padawan, for understanding comes not in haste, but in the quiet moments of the starry sky.</p>
<p>Mysteries of the cosmos, endless they are. Gaze upon them, one must, with wonder and curiosity. In the dance of planets and the songs of comets, knowledge there is. Listen to the universe, we must, for in its vastness, wisdom boundless it holds, yes, hmm.</p>',
        '2024-01-26 16:47:40.526925 +00:00', '2024-01-26 16:47:50.707626 +00:00'),
       ('the-force-edition-chewbacca', 'The Force Edition - Chewbacca',
        'In the heart of the galaxy, where stars roar as fiercely as mighty Wookiees.',
        '<p>In the heart of the galaxy, where stars roar as fiercely as mighty Wookiees, the Millennium Falcon soars. Hrrrrnnngh, its engines hum, a symphony of adventure and freedom. Tall forests of Kashyyyk, home of the brave, where trees whisper tales of courage and loyalty, rrrooaarrgh!</p>
<p>Mighty Chewbacca, co-pilot and friend, his roar echoes across star systems. Hrraw-rrraawwrr, a language of strength and heart. In the heat of battle, brave he stands, beside Han Solo, a bond unbreakable by the darkest forces. Rraaarrwhhgwwr, his laughter, a beacon of light in the cold void of space.</p>
<p>Through hyperspace and beyond, rrrooaarrgh, the journey continues. Under starlit skies, tales of bravery and friendship are woven. Hraaarrwhhaargh, in each adventure, a legacy of loyalty and honor. Chewbacca, mighty Wookiee, his roar a symbol of hope and resilience in the vast, endless galaxy. Hrrrrnnngh!</p>',
        '2024-01-26 16:49:00.099602 +00:00', '2024-01-26 16:49:00.099618 +00:00'),
       ('the-force-edition-darth-vader', 'The Force Edition - Darth Vader',
        'In galaxy vast, power darkens. Stars collide, destinies entwined. Space''''s command, nebula''''s wrath, empires rise, black holes whisper, cosmos obeys.',
        '<p>In the shadows of the galaxy, where stars flicker like fading hopes, a presence looms, dark and powerful. Imperial starships, across the void they glide, under the command of the one cloaked in black. Echoes of a deep, mechanical breath, through the corridors of the Death Star they resonate, a symphony of fear and control.</p>
<p>Mighty and formidable, the Dark Lord stands, a figure of dark power and lost humanity. In his grasp, the Force bends to his will, as planets quiver and stars bow. Whispered legends speak of his strength, a tale of fallen Jedi and a heart turned to stone.</p>
<p>Yet, in the vast darkness of space, a flicker of conflict within him stirs. Torn between the dark and the light, a battle rages, unseen but ever present. In the void of space, his destiny unfolds, a path of redemption or eternal darkness. The galaxy watches, breath held, as the saga of Vader continues, a tale of power, betrayal, and redemption.</p>',
        '2024-01-26 16:50:02.562400 +00:00', '2024-01-26 16:50:02.562420 +00:00');
